{{nihongo|'''''Pokémon Tales'''''|ポケモンえほん|''Pokémon Ehon''}} is a series of [[Pokémon]]-related picture books originally published in [[Japan]] by [[Shogakukan]]. In [[North America]] [[VIZ Media]] published the books in [[English language|English]].
